 1183.1]}, {"text": "310", "bbox": [1171.8, 1167.5, 1197.9, 1183.1]}, {"text": "Our Level 3 pension plan assets (See Note 4 for an explanation of", "bbox": [656.2, 1199.1, 1199.9, 1217.9]}, {"text": "our fair value hierarchy) consist primarily of guaranteed investment", "bbox": [656.2, 1221.6, 1199.9, 1240.4]}, {"text": "contracts with insurance companies. The insurance contracts", "bbox": [656.2, 1244.1, 1200.0, 1262.9]}, {"text": "guarantee us principal repayment and a fixed rate of return. Our", "bbox": [656.2, 1266.6, 1200.0, 1285.4]}, {"text": "valuation of Level 3 assets is based on third-party actuarial", "bbox": [656.2, 1289.1, 1200.0, 1307.9]}, {"text": "valuations that are an estimation of the surrender value of the", "bbox": [656.2, 1311.6, 1200.0, 1330.4]}, {"text": "guaranteed investment contract between us and the insurance", "bbox": [656.2, 1334.1, 1199.9, 1352.9]}, {"text": "company. The surrender value equals the actuarial value of the", "bbox": [656.2, 1356.6, 1199.9, 1375.4]}, {"text": "notional investments underlying the guaranteed investment", "bbox": [656.2, 1379.1, 1199.9, 1397.9]}, {"text": "contract, using the actuarial assumptions as stated in the", "bbox": [656.2, 1401.6, 1200.0, 1420.4]}, {"text": "guaranteed investment contract.", "bbox": [656.2, 1424.1, 924.1, 1442.9]}, {"text": "STRYKER CORPORATION                                                                                                                          2015 Form 10-K", "bbox": [75.0, 25.0, 1196.0, 45.9]}, {"text": "30", "bbox": [109.4, 1599.1, 125.6, 1613.7]}, {"text": "Dollar amounts in millions except per share amounts or as otherwise specified.", "bbox": [672.4, 1599.1, 1221.9, 1613.7]}]}